                <![CDATA[ASUS Zenbook A14]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295693</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ASUS 今日在香港公布推出全新 Zenbook A14 (2025)，这款笔记型电脑主打极致轻量化、强大 AI 整合，及 长效续航力，并搭载 Snapdragon X 系列处理器，适合需要长时间移动工作的专业人士与创作者。Zenbook A14 以 980g 的超轻机身成为目前市场上最轻的 Copilot+ PC，更在硬体设计与 AI 体验上带来显著提升，为使用者提供高效能与便捷性兼备的选择。</p><p><a title="L1000356" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366699459/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366699459_d8af9b4a00_b.jpg" alt="L1000356" width="906" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316-574x580.jpg" alt="" width="574" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316-574x580.jpg 574w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316.jpg 890w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 574px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324-694x546.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="546" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324-694x546.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671-587x580.jpg" alt="" width="587" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671-587x580.jpg 587w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671.jpg 911w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 587px" /></p><p><a title="L1000374" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365623092/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365623092_cd902d1de8_b.jpg" alt="L1000374" width="1024" height="680" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000382" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366498051/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366498051_9fe26dbc4e_b.jpg" alt="L1000382" width="802" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>全球最轻 980g 机身，Ceraluminum 材质提升耐用度</h2><p>Zenbook A14 以，仅 980g 的重量成为目前全球最轻的 Copilot+ PC，同时配备 14 吋荧幕，超越同尺寸竞争对手，如 MacBook Air（1.24kg, 13.6&#8243;） 及 Galaxy Book4 Edge（1.16kg, 14&#8243;），提供更轻巧便携的使用体验。为达到极致轻量化，Zenbook A14 采用 Ceraluminum 陶瓷铝合金机身材质，这种新技术能让机身比传统阳极氧化铝材轻 30%，但强度提升 3 倍，确保笔电在轻盈的同时依然坚固耐用。此外，Ceraluminum 具备防刮、防指纹、抗污，特性，进一步提升机身的耐久性，让使用者即使长期携带，也能保持机身清洁且美观。</p><p><a title="L1000403" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366731198/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366731198_f6f024703d_b.jpg" alt="L1000403" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000394" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365626137/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365626137_a921946396_b.jpg" alt="L1000394" width="723" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295701" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 data-start="956" data-end="991"><strong data-start="960" data-end="989">3K OLED 荧幕与沉浸式音效，视听体验全面升级</strong></h2><p data-start="993" data-end="1155">Zenbook A14 配置 14 吋 3K ASUS Lumina OLED 荧幕，提供更细腻的画面细节与色彩表现，适合专业创作者及高需求视觉体验的用户。笔电支援 Dolby Atmos 与 Snapdragon Sound 音效认证，让用户即使在笔电上，也能享受到如家庭剧院般的沉浸式音效体验。</p><br /><b>
双 USB-C（Thunderbolt）<br />
HDMI<br />
3.5mm 耳机孔<br />
这样的设计让使用者无需额外购买转接器或 Docking，即可轻松连接多种周边设备，提高使用的便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322-643x580.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322-643x580.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322.jpg 997w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318-560x580.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318-560x580.jpg 560w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318.jpg 869w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 560px" /></p><p><a title="L1000381" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366498131/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366498131_b3ce95af60_b.jpg" alt="L1000381" width="786" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>加大触控板，支援智慧手势操作</h2><p>Zenbook A14 配备，加大触控板，并支援，智慧手势操作，使用者可以直接透过触控板来调整，萤幕亮度、音量，甚至，媒体播放控制，让操作更加直觉，提高生产力。</p><br /><b>
智慧搜寻（可依据关键字搜寻图像与文件）<br />
AI 降噪（提升视讯会议音质）<br />
更完整的 Copilot 2.0 整合<br />
ASUS 内置 Studio Coupe 软体，提供，统一化影像管理功能，适合内容创作者与专业设计师使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673-694x548.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="548" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673-694x548.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295702" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>香港市场独家版本与售价</h2><p>Zenbook A14 在香港推出两个版本，售价如下：</p><p>Snapdragon X Elite + 32GB RAM + 1TB SSD：HKD 13,998<br />
Snapdragon X + 32GB RAM + 1TB SSD：HKD 11,998<br />
预购时间：2025 年 3 月 7 日至 3 月 18 日<br />
正式发售：2025 年 3 月 19 日</p><p>预购赠品：</p><p>ASUS AP2600 防刮防水电脑包<br />
MD-102 人体工学滑鼠</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /><a title="L1000399" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366898130/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366898130_276b706ec7_b.jpg" alt="L1000399" width="977" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000401" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366730493/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366730493_e66352a2f7_b.jpg" alt="L1000401" width="1024" height="652" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000364" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365622537/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365622537_7ebf763842_b.jpg" alt="L1000364" width="764" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000352" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365620647/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365620647_c0e7b99d3c_b.jpg" alt="L1000352" width="1024" height="679" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>【ASUS AI – Zenbook A14 手提电脑规格列表