        <item>
            <title>香港 5 的士车队登场，各自推出独立 Call 车 App、叫晒全部需装 5 个 App</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/taxi-need-5-app/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=taxi-need-5-app</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/taxi-need-5-app/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 08:31:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[的士]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295678</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港五间的士车队于 2025 年 3 月 3 日联袂亮相，举行启动礼展示别具一格的车身设计与服务特色。各队车队均设专属 Call 车平台及 Call 车 App，换句说话讲，市民需分别下载五个专属应用程式预约，泰和车行的「JOIE 乐行」预计本月底率先营运，其余四队则于 7 月开始营运。市民需分别预约五个车队，部分人反映若一队有车，需逐一取消其他四队预约，盼未来能整合至单一应用程式，方便召唤所有车队。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295684" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-8-694x381.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="381" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-8-694x381.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202503/03/P2025030300147.htm">香港政府新闻公报</a></p><p>橙色的「JOIE 乐行」规模达 800 辆，气势不凡；星群的士以白红相间示人，拥有 425 辆混合车队；「Amigo」披上萤光粉红与蓝色外衣，计划推出 1,000 辆；「大黄锋」橙红黄色交织，同样坐拥 1,000 辆；Big Boss Taxi 则以深红与黑色豪华车型登场，规模 300 辆。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-6-694x335.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="335" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-6-694x335.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-6-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202503/03/P2025030300147.htm">香港政府新闻公报</a></p><p>星群的士网约价较咪表高出一至两成，「大黄锋」繁忙时段更贵三成，其他车队收费尚待市场试水，力求贴合民情。「JOIE 乐行」设奖罚机制激励司机，「大黄锋」车头屏幕支援多语，Big Boss Taxi 豪华座椅融入按摩功能。《南华早报》2025 年 3 月 5 日指出，政府冀车队提升服务质素，满足多元需求。有网民在网上讨论指，与其逐一下载五个应用程式，不如用单一平台如 Uber 更方便，甚至质疑收费上涨后的吸引力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-7-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-7-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/p2025030300147_photo-7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202503/03/P2025030300147.htm">香港政府新闻公报</a></p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202503/03/P2025030300147.htm">香港政府新闻公报</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20250303/s00001/1740987130510/5%E9%96%93%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%B4-%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B6%B2%E7%B4%84%E5%83%B9%E8%BC%83%E5%92%AA%E8%A1%A8%E5%83%B9%E8%B2%B4%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E6%88%90-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8A%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99">明报</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
