        <item>
            <title>PC  GTA V 免费升级登场，支援 AMD FSR、NVIDIA DLSS</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gtav-pc-free-update</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 06:30:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta 5]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295642</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>RockStar 宣布 PC 版《Grand Theft Auto V》今日推出免费升级，玩家可透过 Rockstar Games Launcher、Steam 或 Epic Games 平台体验。新版本引入先前仅限最新世代主机的功能，并提升现代 PC 的游戏效能。现有玩家可免费升级并转移故事模式及线上模式进度，新玩家购买时则同时获赠强化版与传承版。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118-694x294.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="294" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118-694x294.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次升级为《GTA Online》带来多项新功能，包括 Hao’s Special Works 的全新车辆，如 Pegassi Weaponized Ignus、Coil Cyclone II 超级跑车、 Karin S95 跑车、Arbiter GT 美式肌肉车及 Pfister Astron Custom SUV。此外，20 款原有载具亦可于阿浩特制改装调整性能。为庆祝 GTA+ 登陆 PC，会员可于即日起至 5 月 28 日免费领取 Principe Deveste Eight 超级跑车。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295644" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133-694x292.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="292" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133-694x292.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>玩家更可探索动物生态系统，参与每日野生动物摄影挑战，并透过更新后的启动画面及事业建构器（附 400 万 GTA 游戏币）提升游戏体验。全新更新「Oscar Guzman Flies Again」亦同步上线，提供新任务及飞行载具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新版本针对 PC 玩家推出独有光线追踪功能，包括环境光遮蔽、全域照明及光线追踪阴影与反射，并支援 AMD FSR 及 NVIDIA DLSS（未来将加入影格生成）。配合 SSD 及 DirectStorage 技术，载入速度显著加快，同时支援更高画质、更高解像度及 Dolby Atmos 音效，语音方面有所提升，支援电影音乐及特效等。玩家更可可体验自适应扳机的 DualSense 控制器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/7551a7k917554a/free-upgrade-for-grand-theft-auto-v-on-pc-now-available">Rockstar Games</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/">PC  GTA V 免费升级登场，支援 AMD FSR、NVIDIA DLSS</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
